OL,3,CCompany fined after father-of-two
OL,4,Ckilled by escaped cow
OL,6,FA company has been fined #75,000 after
OL,7,Fa 75-year-old man was killed by a cow
OL,8,Fthat had escaped from a livestock
OL,9,Fmarket.
OL,11,FHuw Evans, a father of two, was
OL,12,Fknocked down and trampled by a cow
OL,13,Fthat was being auctioned at a
OL,14,Flivestock market run by J.J. Morris
OL,15,FLimited on November 19, 2022.JThe cow
OL,16,Fwas being unloaded into a pen at
OL,17,FWhitland Livestock Market in
OL,18,FCarmarthenshire, but managed to escape
OL,19,Fbefore heading towards Whitland town
OL,20,Fcentre.
