OL,6,FMr Evans had been crossing the
OL,7,Fjunction at North Road and West Street
OL,8,Fwhen he was attacked by the cow.JHe
OL,9,Fsuffered multiple injuries and was
OL,10,Fflown to the University Hospital of
OL,11,FWales, but died died six days later.
