OL,6,FA worker at J.J. Morris Limited was
OL,7,Finjured in an attempt to capture the
OL,8,Fcow, before it was caught and put down
OL,9,Fby Dyfed-Powys Police.JA Health and
OL,10,FSafety Executive (HSE) investigation
OL,11,Ffound J.J. Morris Limited, which has
OL,12,Foperated Whitland Livestock Market for
OL,13,Fmore than 30 years, failed to
OL,14,Fimplement basic, physical control
OL,15,Fmeasures to prevent cattle from
OL,16,Fescaping.
