OL,6,FMr Evans' son, Dafydd, told the court:
OL,7,F"Dad was my best friend and I miss him
OL,8,Fterribly, he was taken from us too
OL,9,Fsoon. Losing dad has had a tremendous
OL,10,Feffect on both myself and my brother.
OL,12,F"Because of this incident dad's
OL,13,Fgrandsons will never fully know him
OL,14,Fpersonally and he will not see them
OL,15,Fgrow up."JRhys Hughes, a HSE
OL,16,Finspector, said after the hearing:
OL,17,F"This tragic incident was foreseeable
OL,18,Fand preventable. The risk posed by
OL,19,Fcattle escaping from the livestock
OL,20,Fmart should have been identified, and
OL,21,Feffective control measures implemented.
